title: Hi Dracula
overview: Hi Dracula is the growth story of people who live in Block Z who have to face the matters in life that they just want to avoid. It's an omnibus drama about a daughter named Anna who gives in to her mother, a mother named Ji Young who overpowers her daughter, an indie band vocalist named Seo Yun, born rich Ji Hyung and Yoo Ra, who wasn't brought up in the best of conditions.
